      "raceComments": "{\"comment\":\"8. BETTY ROSE returns from a three months break after failing to finish at this track last time but prior to that was a 27.70 winner here in a Mix. Suited here and worth another try fresh. 2. COPY THAT was safely held last time out, finishing fifth at Grafton over 450m behind Magical Saide (26.25) in a Grade 5. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings two times from three attempts. Bold showing expected. 3. WATCH THE DIVA boasts a strong record this journey here with two wins and two minors from six tries. Was out of the placings last time (20.56) at Grafton in a Grade 5, finishing seventh and beaten 10 lengths. Suited here and expected to run well. 1. FLORELLA can play a role in the finish without surprising.\",\"runners\":[8,2,3,1],\"exclusive\":false}",
